name: million little reasons
description:
The artwork story :

There are a million little reasons why I like your smile
There are a million little reasons why I like your style
If I try to write it down
I will run out of ink
There are a million little reasons why I want you here
There are a million little reasons why I want you close
If I try to write it down
I will run out of cigarettes

digital painting
